### Tour Guide Management API Tests

### 1. Register a new Tour Guide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/register-tourguide
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userName": "guide1",
    "email": "guide1@example.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "address": "123 Guide Street",
    "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
    "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar1.jpg"
}

### 2. Hide the Tour Guide (set IsActive to false)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguide-status
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourGuideId": 1,
    "isActive": false
}

### 3. Debug: Check email status before registration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/debug/check-email?email=guide1@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 4. Debug: Check email status after hiding tour guide
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/debug/check-email?email=guide1@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 5. Register another Tour Guide with same email (should work if previous account is inactive)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/register-tourguide
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userName": "guide2",
    "email": "guide1@example.com",
    "password": "654321",
    "address": "456 Guide Avenue",
    "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
    "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar2.jpg"
}

### 5.1. Debug: Check email status after registration (should show only new account)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/debug/check-email?email=guide1@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 6. Get list of Tour Guides
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguides?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 7. Get list of active Tour Guides only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguides?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 8. Get list of inactive Tour Guides only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguides?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&isActive=false
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 9. Get list of all Tour Guides (both active and inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguides?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&showInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 10. Search Tour Guides by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguides?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&username=guide
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}

### 11. Show a Tour Guide (set IsActive to true)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/TourOperator/tourguide-status
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourGuideId": 2,
    "isActive": true
}

### Variables (set these in your environment)
# @baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
# @tourOperatorToken = your_jwt_token_here 